race.comment: RUNAMILEINMYSHOES (8) finished out of the money when fresh from a spell two starts back then she got a long way back and was beaten 8 lengths when 11th over 1609m at Del Mar five weeks ago. Yet to miss the frame in seven starts over this course and distance. Faces an easier assignment so she is likely to play a big role. SUMMER LAKE (4) kicked off this campaign with a win two runs ago. Less impressive last time out when 12th over 1308m at Del Mar, beaten 21 lengths. Beautifully placed and is sure to prove tough to beat. BREVE (3) was always well out of her ground when 1.75 lengths from the winner in fifth over 1609m at Del Mar last start, a less impressive effort than her fourth at Del Mar the run before. Faces an easier assignment so she is perfectly placed to score. ISSA COURT (6) was unplaced two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1609m at Del Mar, beaten 4 lengths into fourth. Nicely placed to find some form.
